parameters: The bottom of the hole is shallow, but the side holes look deep...
There are cobwebs all over the place.
There you are, the pear of the sacred tree.
I'm glad I was able to retrieve it.
I knew you had a nest!
How dare you smoke me out earlier?
Well, I don't want to go toe to toe with you.
There was a nest nearby, you know, just in case.
And yet you are destined to be born to me!
I'm more and more tempted to use you as my mother.
You still have that kind of energy?
Get out of the way so I can miss you!
No way, there's a nest nearby!
If you'd been right above me, I might have seen you.
I don't know if I can turn him away on my own...
Can you escape my filthy mucus?
I'm more and more tempted to use you as my mother.
You still have that kind of energy?
Get out of the way so I can miss you!
It's a dead tree that seems to burn well...
There's a dead tree growing there that seems to burn well...
Do you want to burn it with fire?
Really, I don't know if I can...
What?　You want to fight me?
I guess that's what you get for flying into the fire.
If you're not going to be a mother, you need to leave.
I'll come back to punish you, okay?
Oh, my God. I love this place.
No, I'm not talking about the location...
I'll nether you anytime you want...
I don't want to do that.
There's a stone monument. We'll be safe here!
Do you want to consume the bonfire set and rest?
Huh?　I don't have any of those.。
We'll consume one bonfire set, if that's all right.
